The '''Artists' High Commune''' was located on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Mrlsst/Legends|Mrlsst]] in the [[Tapani sector/Legends|Tapani sector]]. It was built at the top of [[Greenstalk]] [[Tree/Legends|trees]] and was the home of Mrlsst's misfits, artists, poets and dropouts. Members of [[Rogue Squadron/Legends|Rogue Squadron]] used the commune to hide when they were implicated in stealing the [[Phantom Project]] [[Starship/Legends|ship]] [[Datacard/Legends|datacards]].

